text: Brendan Dolan (born 30 November 1966) is an Irish rower. He competed in the men's lightweight double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Ireland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
